Package myservs

Class Summary
AddProject Servlet class implementing AddProject feature which adds a project to user's personal repository.
AdminChangeData Administrator servlet class which implements the administration ability to change personal data of the registered users.
Auxiliary Class that implements all the auxiliary methods needed.
CaseDel Administrator servlet class that deletes a case from the database.
ChangePersonalData Servlet class implementation for the change of personal data of the users.
CheckLogin Servlet implementation class which checks if the user's credentials are correct.
DatabaseMethods Class that implements all the methods that query the database.
Download Servlet implementation class which produces a downloadable file with specific version from any project owned.
EditCase Administrator servlet implementation class which update a case in database.
MakeAdmin Administration servlet implementation class which switches states of a user between administrator or regular user.
Publish Servlet implementation class for publishing a case.
Register Servlet implementation class Register which registers a user
UserDel Administration servlet implementation class UserDel which deletes a user from the system.
